Package sample

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Chassis
    Interface of the Chassis - frame of the car.
    Engine
    Holds the setters and getters for the Engine features of the vehicle.
    Feature
    Interface that holds methods for features on cars.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Car
    Final class Car that extends to another concrete class Vehicle.
    Controller  
    ExteriorFeature
    Concrete class for the exterior features of the car, implements the getters and setters from Feature.
    InteriorFeature
    Concrete class for interior feature of the vehicle.
    Main
    Main class prints out "Whatzzup Vanselow".
    ManufacturedEngine
    Class holds all the features for the implemented interface Engine.
    Vehicle
    Class Vehicle takes all features from Engine and Chassis.
    VehicleChassis
    This class access Chassis interface and gets its name and type and prints it out.
    VehicleFrame
    This class focuses on the vehicle frame and takes inputs from Chassis(interface).
